      <akn:section eId="sec_38_826_05">
        <akn:num>38-826.05</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Tobacco-free school campuses.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_38-826_05_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Tobacco and tobacco products are prohibited in public school and public charter school buildings, grounds, parking lots, parking garages, playing fields, school buses and other vehicles, and at off-campus, school-sponsored events.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_38-826_05_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>For a public charter school located in a mixed-use facility, the requirements of subsection (a) of this section shall apply only to the buildings, grounds, parking lots, garages, and fields under the control of the public charter school.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
